%
O0001
; THE BEAST - Move 1" Right and Return
; Feed Rate: 100 in/min | Plunge: 80 in/min | Spindle: 22000 RPM

G20        ; Inches mode
G90        ; Absolute mode
G91        ; Switch to relative positioning
S22000     ; Spindle speed
M3         ; Spindle ON
G4 P2      ; Dwell 2 seconds - let spindle spin up
F80        ; Plunge rate 80 in/min
G1 Z-0.1  ; Lower Z 0.1 inches
F100       ; Switch to feed rate 100 in/min
G1 X1.0   ; Move 1 inch to the right
G1 X-1.0  ; Return 1 inch back to start
M5         ; Spindle OFF
G90        ; Return to absolute positioning
M30        ; End program and rewind
%
